dct_description_sm: compiled, drawn and photographed by Directorate of Overseas Surveys.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
Includes compilation diagram, sheet history and sheet index.

Map of South Orkney Islands showing trigonometrical and astronometrical stations, traverses, rocks, areas of rocks and broken water, coastlines, areas exposed at low water, beaches above high water, summits, cliffs, areas free of permanent snow and ice, seasonal streams, lakes, moraines, and buildings.
